Liu Ye, Zhang Ziyi receive Order of Arts and Letters
2013-06-28 02:52:15 GMT
Chinese movie stars Liu Ye, Zhang Ziyi were awarded the Order of Arts and Letters by the French government in Beijing, capital of China, June 27, 2013. Established in 1957, the order is the recognition of significant contributions to the arts and literature.Liu kissed his French wife after receiving the award.
